function_TestXAIProvider_ReturnsValidPro.name: TestXAIProvider_ReturnsValidProvider
function_TestXAIProvider_ReturnsValidPro.content:
func TestXAIProvider_ReturnsValidProvider(t *testing.T) {
	t.Parallel()
	provider := XAIProvider(nil)

	require.NotEmpty(t, provider.ID)
	require.Equal(t, "xai", string(provider.ID))
	require.Equal(t, "xAI", provider.Name)
	requireValidProvider(t, provider)
}

func TestXAIProvider_HasGrokModels(t *testing.T) {
	t.Parallel()
	provider := XAIProvider(nil)

	require.Len(t, provider.Models, 6)
	require.Equal(t, "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning", string(provider.Models[0].ID))
	require.Equal(t, "Grok 4.1 Fast Reasoning", provider.Models[0].Name)
}
